Enum CefApp.CefAppState

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<CefApp.CefAppState>
      • org.cef.CefApp.CefAppState
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<CefApp.CefAppState>
    Enclosing class:
    CefApp 

    public static enum CefApp.CefAppState
extends java.lang.Enum<CefApp.CefAppState>
    The CefAppState gives you a hint if the CefApp is already usable or not usable any more. See values for details.(CefAppState可以让您了解CefApp的各种状态。有关详细信息，请参见值。)

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      INITIALIZATION_FAILED
      CEF initialization has failed (for example due to a second process using the same root_cache_path).(CEF初始化失败（例如，由于第二个进程使用相同的root_cache_path）。)
      INITIALIZED
      CefApp is up and running.(CefApp已经启动并运行。)
      INITIALIZING
      CefApp is in its initializing process.(CefApp正在初始化过程中。)
      NEW
      CefApp is new created but not initialized yet.(CefApp是新创建的，但尚未初始化。)
      NONE
      No CefApp instance was created yet.(尚未创建CefApp实例。)
      SHUTTING_DOWN
      CefApp is in its shutdown process.(CefApp正在关闭过程中。)
      TERMINATED
      CefApp is terminated and can't be used any more.(CefApp已终止，无法再使用。)

    • Enum Constant Detail

      • INITIALIZATION_FAILED

        public static final CefApp.CefAppState INITIALIZATION_FAILED
        CEF initialization has failed (for example due to a second process using the same root_cache_path).(CEF初始化失败（例如，由于第二个进程使用相同的root_cache_path）。)

      • INITIALIZED

        public static final CefApp.CefAppState INITIALIZED
        CefApp is up and running. At least one CefClient was created and the message loop is running. You can use all classes and methods of JCEF now.(CefApp已启动并运行。此时至少创建了一个CefClient，并且消息循环正在运行。您现在可以使用JCEF的所有类和方法了。)

      • INITIALIZING

        public static final CefApp.CefAppState INITIALIZING
        CefApp is in its initializing process. Please wait until initializing is finished.(CefApp正在初始化过程中，请等待初始化完成。)

      • NEW

        public static final CefApp.CefAppState NEW
        CefApp is new created but not initialized yet. No CefClient and no CefBrowser was created until now.(CefApp是新创建的并且尚未初始化，此时还没有创建CefClient和CefBrowser。)

      • NONE

        public static final CefApp.CefAppState NONE
        No CefApp instance was created yet. Call getInstance() to create a new one.(尚未创建CefApp实例，您可以调用getInstance()创建一个新实例。)

      • SHUTTING_DOWN

        public static final CefApp.CefAppState SHUTTING_DOWN
        CefApp is in its shutdown process. All CefClients and CefBrowser instances will be disposed. No new CefClient or CefBrowser is allowed to be created. The message loop will be performed until all CefClients and all CefBrowsers are disposed completely.(CefApp正在关闭中，所有CefClients和CefBrowser实例都将被释放。此时不允许创建新的CefClient或CefBrowser，消息循环将持续运行，直到所有CefClients和CefBrowser被完全释放。)

      • TERMINATED

        public static final CefApp.CefAppState TERMINATED
        CefApp is terminated and can't be used any more. You can shutdown the application safely now.(CefApp已终止，无法再使用。您现在可以安全地关闭应用程序。)
